metadata.name: Saturn // Surfer
metadata.description:
MP4 Format // Sound on.

Outer space is not only outside the earth, it's everywhere around us waiting to be discovered.

Saturn is a representation of my ever-changing state of mind, moving from one plane to another.

With music by Fabian Winandi, we try to capture interplanetary warfare that happens inside our own mind.

We can no longer live in a single reality, we are multidimensional creatures who lives in the real world, connecting digitally, and slowly migrating to the Meta World.
